column2: SELECT    gal.run, gal.camCol, gal.field, gal.objID, gal.ra, gal.dec, s.z,   gal.raErr, gal.decErr, s.zErr, s.zwarning,   s.class, s.sourcetype. s.firstrelease INTO mydb.LRG_SAMPLE_CHANGE_withspec FROM Galaxy as gal   JOIN specobj as s ON s.bestobjid = gal.objid WHERE ( ( flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) ) > #     and ( flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) ) != dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)     and ( flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) ) = #     and (gal.petroMag_r > # and gal.g > # and gal.r > # and gal.i > #)     and ( (gal.petroMag_r-gal.extinction_r) < #       and (gal.petroMag_r - gal.extinction_r < (# + (# * (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r) + # * (gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i) - # * #)/#) )         and ( (gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i - (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r)/# - #) < #)       and ( (gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i - (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r)/# - #) > #)       and ( (gal.petroMag_r - gal.extinction_r + # * LOG1#(# * # * gal.petror5#_r * gal.petror5#_r)) < #) )     or  ( (gal.petroMag_r - gal.extinction_r < #)       and ( (gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i - (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r)/# - #) > (# - (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r)/#) )       and ( (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r) > (# + # * (gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i)) )        and ( (gal.petroMag_r - gal.extinction_r + # * LOG1#(# * # * gal.petror5#_r * gal.petror5#_r) ) < # ) ) )
